aukati
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:. [Aukati ... 3. n. Line which one may not pass.] Mainly as attrib., with boundary, line, pole, a line which may not be passed or crossed. (Cf cut n. f. Ma. kati.)
Origin:
